{"tid":2417603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［恆河變種］印度發現新型變種病毒株 專家：高達240種","createTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T04:40:36.000Z","uid":60585,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"639dbad1d688f4553d8b87484d8ea6626a85fd77","tid":2417603,"uid":60585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"2021/02/22 10:15<br />\n<br />\n印度發現新型變種病毒株 專家：高達240種<br />\n印度發現新型變種病毒株 專家：高達240種 | 華視新聞<br />\n吳念達 綜合報導  / 印度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCOVID-19疫情爆發以來，英國、南非以及巴西等國，陸續出現感染力更強的新型變種病毒，而印度衛生官員日前更表示，在印度境內竟發現多達240種的新型變種病毒株，呼籲需積極採取應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n印度發現新型變種病毒 種類高達240種<br />\n<br />\n根據《Rossiya Segodnya》報導，印度權威醫學研究和臨床機構全印醫學科學研究所(AIIMS)主任古雷利亞(Randeep Guleria)表示，在目前已發現的240種新型變種病毒中，<span class=\"blue\">部分變種病毒具有很高的傳染性，甚至更為致命，因為某些變種病毒株已具有免疫的「逃避機制」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n變種病毒再增強 專家：接種疫苗者恐再次染疫<br />\n<br />\n古雷利亞進一步表示，這些變種病毒的強度，足以使部分具有抗體或者已經接種疫苗的人再次染疫，當局必續極採取應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/202102/202102222032063.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.cts.com.tw%2Fcts%2Finternational%2F202102%2F202102222032063.html&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=4b5f8765\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.cts.com.tw/cts/international/202102/202102222032063.html</a>"},{"pid":"4494976d9332c27036c3ab171ce6230b62b51fcc","tid":2417603,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"小粉9：終於等到啦，全部人大大聲講「印度肺炎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27a05931605447bd4a58154c35630aa132024f9","tid":2417603,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"阿南德在最新預言指出，2021年2月太陽、月亮、水星、木星、金星、土星會形成罕見的六星連珠，可能會帶來驚人災難，甚至經濟崩潰，直至11月才有轉機。"},{"pid":"c957b4b2df5d8cd3ca2a6a9ccb2696133ac30271","tid":2417603,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"240種<br />\n牛逼死了<br />\n有冇病毒學家講下以前有咩病毒有咁牛逼"},{"pid":"335a1acbc31bc8a0eb8b6c7868fc7b5899b6a6e8","tid":2417603,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:39:05.000Z","msg":"印度世界第一"},{"pid":"3f7f484e6ba3daaf6c932fb0dc4ed1d90990f4bc","tid":2417603,"uid":273545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c957b4b2df5d8cd3ca2a6a9ccb2696133ac30271","tid":2417603,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"240種<br />\n牛逼死了<br />\n有冇病毒學家講下以前有咩病毒有咁牛逼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"牛你老母 死大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03c32de0bf814950020028d4968deb83514d7e9","tid":2417603,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3f7f484e6ba3daaf6c932fb0dc4ed1d90990f4bc","tid":2417603,"uid":273545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c957b4b2df5d8cd3ca2a6a9ccb2696133ac30271","tid":2417603,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:27.000Z","msg":"240種<br />\n牛逼死了<br />\n有冇病毒學家講下以前有咩病毒有咁牛逼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:40:14.000Z","msg":"牛你老母 死大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}